OL,3,C'Deeply concerned': British couple
OL,4,Cdetained in Iran charged with espionage
OL,6,FEarlier this week, Iran's state-run
OL,7,Fmedia said the couple had been accused
OL,8,Fof security-related offences, ITV News
OL,9,FCorrespondent Martha Fairlie reports
OL,11,FThe Foreign Office has said it is
OL,12,F"deeply concerned" about a British
OL,13,Fcouple who have been detained in Iran
OL,14,Fand charged with espionage.
OL,16,FCraig and Lindsay Foreman were
OL,17,Freportedly arrested by Iranian
OL,18,Fauthorities in January while
OL,19,Ftravelling by motorcycle around the
OL,20,Fworld, despite Foreign Office advice
OL,21,Fagainst visiting the country.
