OL,3,C'Deeply concerned': British couple
OL,4,Cdetained in Iran charged with espionage
OL,6,FA Foreign Office spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"We are deeply concerned by reports
OL,8,Fthat two British nationals have been
OL,9,Fcharged with espionage in Iran.
OL,11,F"We continue to raise this case
OL,12,Fdirectly with the Iranian authorities.
OL,14,F"We are providing them with consular
OL,15,Fassistance and remain in close contact
OL,16,Fwith their family members."
OL,18,FIranian authorities claim the couple
OL,19,Fposed as tourists to gather
OL,20,Finformation for "covert institutions".
