OL,6,F"The individuals arrested entered Iran
OL,7,Funder the guise of tourists and, under
OL,8,Fthe guise of research and
OL,9,Finvestigation work, have collected
OL,10,Finformation in several provinces of
OL,11,Fthe country," a spokesperson for
OL,12,FIran's judiciary said.
OL,14,F"These individuals were cooperating
OL,15,Fwith covert institutions related to
OL,16,Fthe intelligence services of hostile
OL,17,Fand Western countries under the guise
OL,18,Fof research and investigation
OL,19,Factivities.
