OL,6,F"These two British citizens were
OL,7,Farrested and placed under the control
OL,8,Fof the provincial intelligence
OL,9,Fagencies during a series of
OL,10,Fcoordinated intelligence operations
OL,11,Fand while collecting information in
OL,12,FKerman city."
OL,14,FOn Saturday, their family said the
OL,15,Fsituation was causing "significant
OL,16,Fconcern".
OL,18,FMr and Mrs Foreman were ultimately
OL,19,Fheading for Australia, having crossed
OL,20,Finto Iran from Armenia on December 30,
OL,21,Faccording to social media posts.
