OL,6,FThe couple ` originally from Forest
OL,7,FRow, near East Grinstead in Sussex `
OL,8,Fmoved to Spain in 2019
OL,10,FMrs Foreman was said to be carrying
OL,11,Fout a research project as part of the
OL,12,Fjourney, asking people what
OL,13,Fconstitutes a "good life".
OL,15,FThe couple had shared a number of
OL,16,Fupdates from Iran and had been
OL,17,Fplanning to enter Pakistan next.
OL,19,F"To put your minds at rest, we are
OL,20,Fhaving the most amazing time in Iran,"
OL,21,Fthey posted on Facebook on January 3.
