OL,6,F"From the vast deserts of Iran to the
OL,7,Ftowering peaks of Pakistan, we hope to
OL,8,Fshare the beauty, hospitality, and
OL,9,Fhumanity that often go unnoticed."
OL,11,FBritish citizens have previously been
OL,12,Fheld by the Iranian regime.
OL,14,FNazanin Zaghari-Ratcliffe and Annosheh
OL,15,FAshoori, who are dual British-Iranian
OL,16,Fcitizens, were released in March 2022
OL,17,Fafter being held for several years in
OL,18,FIranian prisons.
